
            *Hydra with Dictionary Attack*
            
- hydra -L <file> -P <file> <ipAddress> ssh -v -d -f
- For individual scans, it works well.

To show attempts:
- hydra -L <file> -P <file> <ipAddress> ssh -v -d -f
- -v: Show service-related details.
- -V: Show attempts.

You can also launch Hydra and use the graphical interface by typing 'hydra'.